{"tid":800396,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴比亞迪電動巴唔夠電行全日　9月28日起更改行駛路線","createTime":"2018-08-30T23:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T10:32:10.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79387dbeb4673507b13651063d3e2dd69d04931f","tid":800396,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T23:58:57.000Z","msg":"政府早年資助專營巴士公司購置36輛單層電動巴士，其中九巴獲分配10輛國產比亞迪電動巴，並於去年7月起至今年1月載客試行走5條路線。惟環保署表示，現階段試驗結果顯示，電動巴士的電池量未足以應付部分路線的全日營運需求，因此由9月28日起調整試驗路線，以評估電動巴在本地環境下的運作效能及表現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1806054/org/8dc82e05d8b5cfa93d748f2b4679f352.jpg/pN7Bh-uz8scCP7zXIaoWr8OrC6N0orySyeSv38nkr98?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1806054%2Forg%2F8dc82e05d8b5cfa93d748f2b4679f352.jpg%2FpN7Bh-uz8scCP7zXIaoWr8OrC6N0orySyeSv38nkr98%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=7906d257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴在政府資助下獲分配10輛單層電池電動巴。(讀者提供)<br />\n<br />\n環保署向區議會提交文件表示，在路線調整後，九巴會以編訂班次行走相關路線以取代原有的單層柴油巴士。有關路線調整包括，現時行走尖沙嘴碼頭至慈雲山(中)的5C線電動巴士，將改為行走7M樂富至竹園邨；行走6C的電動巴士改為行走11D樂富至觀塘碼頭等。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，九巴比亞迪電動巴士過去不時發生故障，其中去年7月一輛行走5C線的電動巴，首班原訂由慈雲山開往尖沙嘴，但到達第一個分站已「跪低」，車上乘客需轉乘另一架巴士。另外，去年6月一輛九巴比亞迪電動巴在路面測試期間出現故障，要由工程車拖走，需要立即送回廠檢查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1805266/org/b62d797d0e4fa3da882900205d9b1a24.jpg/H3qoXgJamnH5FTNbPy87mK0CQNEx17JmCqx22Qqsdtk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1805266%2Forg%2Fb62d797d0e4fa3da882900205d9b1a24.jpg%2FH3qoXgJamnH5FTNbPy87mK0CQNEx17JmCqx22Qqsdtk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f03dd5b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1805022/org/c327e9858b54e576a65abb4fe241adf8.jpg/Z-6uquwWnABi6-JUbEK5REOuTxOevRwAXcNLfl3DS34?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1805022%2Forg%2Fc327e9858b54e576a65abb4fe241adf8.jpg%2FZ-6uquwWnABi6-JUbEK5REOuTxOevRwAXcNLfl3DS34%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f221d800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年7月一輛行走5C線的九巴電動巴故障。（網民「3M_K230UB」圖片）<br />\n<br />\n撰文：潘嘉寶<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/228993/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E%E8%BF%AA%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%B4%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E9%9B%BB%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%97%A5-9%E6%9C%8828%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E8%A1%8C%E9%A7%9B%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F228993%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%25AF%2594%25E4%25BA%259E%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5-9%25E6%259C%258828%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2594%25B9%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%25A7%259B%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A&d=072fkaJ4UVi5TGaQXQwwkAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=9feaea3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/228993/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E%E8%BF%AA%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%B4%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E9%9B%BB%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%97%A5-9%E6%9C%8828%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E8%A1%8C%E9%A7%9B%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A</a>"},{"pid":"b394b3cdeede09b5bbb226bd18f602eedc6e7de6","tid":800396,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9303206d8f8c982bee7b64fb5acdf4b4602b3e","tid":800396,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:14:25.000Z","msg":"甩皮甩骨都要迫你用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09731373c88f7d25f3d13610c7736c015501b8a","tid":800396,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bc9303206d8f8c982bee7b64fb5acdf4b4602b3e","tid":800396,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c